        NAV {
            bindings = <
&none   &none   &none   &kp LEFT_CONTROL  &kp LEFT_SHIFT  &none     &none              &kp PAGE_DOWN       &kp UP_ARROW  &kp PAGE_UP    &none             &none
&trans  &trans  &trans  &trans            &trans          &none     &mt LC(HOME) HOME  &kp LEFT_ARROW      &kp DOWN      &kp RIGHT      &mt LC(END) END   &none
